  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ski Holidays in Bulgaria</strong></p>
<p>Our <a href="https://www.inghams.co.ukk/ski-holidays/">Ski</a> Bulgaria programme offers a wonderfully friendly and warm welcome. Whether you're an absolute novice or a seasoned skier, there's something very special waiting for you when you ski Bulgaria.  If you want to try <a href="https://www.inghams.co.ukk/ski-holidays/">ski holidays</a> in Bulgaria, you'll enjoy all the reassurance that a top quality, comprehensive skiing package offers.</p>
<p><strong>Our Bulgaria ski resorts</strong></p>
<p>Inghams <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/">ski</a> holidays offer some beautiful Bulgarian ski resorts. High in the stunning Pirin Mountains, <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/resorts/hotels/item72/bansko/">Bansko</a> is a lovely old town with fantastic skiing all around. You'll discover wonderful skiing in Bulgaria at lovely <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/resorts/hotels/item139/borovets/">Borovets</a>, deep in the Rila Mountains, a great value resort with easy to access slopes.</p>
<p>With Inghams you can arrange and hire your ski equipment, lessons and lift passes before you go. It's convenient, fast and efficient. You don't have to waste precious holiday time booking equipment when you get there. And you don't have to carry huge amounts of skiing gear with you when you travel. And you can relax in the knowledge that a friendly, expert Ski Bulgaria rep will be on hand in case you need help.</p>
<p><strong>Ski Bulgaria</strong></p>
<p>Ski Bulgaria for a huge range of extra non ski activities. From swimming pools to spa centres, skidoos and traditional feasting, <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/">skiing holidays</a> in Bulgaria deliver much more fun and variety than you might think. Explore this site for full details of our Ski Bulgaria programme including our specially chosen Bulgaria ski resorts, holiday options and accommodation choices. Then book with us online. It's fast and easy. Welcome to ski Bulgaria!</p>]]></description>
